    <item>
      <title>芝加哥耗资 85 亿美元的奥黑尔机场升级计划因成本膨胀而举步维艰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/chicago-s-8-5-billion-o-hare-upgrade-falters-as-costs-balloon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥已经受到人口下降和主要雇主流失的困扰，正在努力推进耗资 85 亿美元的机场升级工程，这对于巩固其作为重要航空枢纽的地位至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/chicago-s-8-5-billion-o-hare-upgrade-falters-as-costs-balloon</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
